5|$|Barbree is {{the author}} or {{coauthor}} of seven books, including two memoirs. In 1993, Shepard, fellow Mercury astronaut Deke Slayton, journalist Howard Benedict, and Barbree collaborated to <b>write</b> <b>the</b> <b>book</b> Moon Shot. Slayton was a participant in name only and died before the book was completed.|$|E
